room_title: Escape room "The Office Of Dr. Landau" by Epic Escape Game in Muncie
room_description:
Dr. Landau is an esteemed surgeon with a practice in the middle of town. Mystery surrounds the doctor after several of his patients have turned up missing. In every case, Dr. Landau has been exonerated and found not connected to his patient’s disappearance.
You have been hired by the family of one of the missing patients to investigate Dr. Landau. While the doctor is out on errands, you sneak into his office only find that you have been locked in. Can you escape in time before you become the doctor’s next patient?
